display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>. We must show that for every <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[i\in {\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, there exists some <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  A]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[!_A{\mathopen {}\left (x\right )\mathclose {}}=i]]></fr:tex>. Letting <fr:tex
