display="inline"><![CDATA[u={\mathopen {}\left  [a\right  ]\mathclose {}}_{E}=q{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> for some <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
